Project#1: Triage - Infra GCP portal development
Client:  Merck & Co
Duration: AUG 2014 – SEP 2016
Project Overview
		Infra GCP portal development project is an enhancement and support project which is a Merck in-house application where Merck employees, agents and contractors use this for Merck infrastructure activities like tracking, monitoring, creating new groups, etc.
Responsibilities:
•	As a team member, I am responsible to do development or support activities for the infra portal tool.
•	Involved in Bug fixing and monitoring the issues/defects tracking and resolve the defects given by team lead.
•	Maintaining SLA for all the incident and critical tickets. 
•	Independent worker for change request/production issues for my developed code.
•	Gathering technical requirements with lead for new dashboard portal enhancements/change requests.

Tools and Technologies
•	HTML, CSS3, JavaScript, AJAX Jquery and Oracle.
•	IDE: Eclipse Luna
•	Server: Apache Tomcat Server 6.0
